---
import FoodServiceLayout from "./FoodServiceLayout.astro";
import beefRavioliImage from "../../../assets/images/perth-food-photography/Beef-Check-Ravioli_01-scaled.jpg";
---

<FoodServiceLayout
  imageSrc={beefRavioliImage}
  imageAlt="Perth restaurant food photography – plated beef ravioli dish"
>
  <header class="food-service__heading">
    <p class="food-service__eyebrow">Food photography for</p>
    <h2 class="food-service__title">Restaurants &amp; Cafés</h2>
  </header>

  <div class="food-service__copy">
    <!-- MERGED INTRO COPY (from PerthFoodPhotographyIntro.astro) -->
    <p>
      As a <strong>Perth food photographer</strong>, we create high-impact
      visuals for restaurants, cafés, food products and hospitality brands. From
      styled hero dishes to menu-ready plates, our photography is designed to
      increase appetite appeal and drive more bookings and sales.
    </p>

    <p>
      Hospitality clients choose us for imagery that blends creativity with
      strategy—photos that look beautiful but also improve menu conversions,
      elevate branding and help customers choose you faster.
    </p>

    <p>
      If you also need product images, explore our
      <a href="/perth-product-photography/">Perth Product Photography</a> services,
      or pair your visuals with a conversion-focused
      <a href="/perth-website-development/">website development</a> project so your
      menu photos look just as good online.
    </p>

    <!-- EXISTING SECTION COPY -->
    <p>
      Don’t let bland photos hurt your business.
      <strong>
        If your menu, website, Google Business Profile or delivery platforms
        like Uber Eats and DoorDash are relying on low-quality images, you’re
        leaving sales on the table.
      </strong>
    </p>

    <p>
      Stunning, mouth-watering imagery is an art form and a crucial part of
      making your venue a must-visit.
      <strong>
        We create premium food photography for Perth restaurants, cafés, bars
        and food trucks – from hero dishes to full-table spreads and interior
        lifestyle shots.
      </strong>
    </p>

    <p>
      <strong>Visually captivating stories:</strong>
      We photograph plated dishes, ingredients, chefs, staff and your venue so diners
      can experience your atmosphere before they ever walk in. Every image is crafted
      to look great across menus, websites and social media.
    </p>

    <p>
      <strong>Stress-free shoot:</strong>
      We work around your service times, bring professional lighting and guide you
      through the process so your team can focus on what they do best – creating incredible
      food – while we capture imagery that drives bookings and online orders.
    </p>
  </div>

  <a href="/contact/" class="food-service__button"> CONTACT </a>
</FoodServiceLayout>
